text: A State of Madness () is a 2020 Dominican Republic drama movie directed by Leticia Tonos and starring Luis José Germán, Jane Santos, Pavel Marcano, Ico Abreu, Rick Montero. ==Other websites== * Category:2020 drama movies Category:Dominican Republic movies Category:Movies set in the Dominican Republic Category:Movies directed by Leticia Tonos
